    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1875-02-24T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1875-02-24T00:00:00-05:00" n="102" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d102">
                <head>(M. 3294.)<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Messrs. <persName type="from">D.
                                    &amp; C. MacIver</persName> to <gloss type="to">Board of
                                    Trade</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">British
                                        and North American Royal Mail Steam-Packet
                                        Company</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Office</hi> 8 <hi rend="italic">Water Street, Liverpool</hi>
                        </placeName>,
                                    <date calendar="gregorian" when="1875-02-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">February</hi> 24, 1875</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: In reply to your communication of the 19th
                            instant, we beg to say that we have referred the matter to Messrs.
                            Burns, of Glasgow, and that their reply to a similar communication from
                            you sufficiently expresses our views upon the subject.</p>
                <p>Yours, &amp;c.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <list>
                            <item>D. &amp; C. M<hi rend="smallcaps">ac</hi>IVER,</item>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="italic">Pro</hi> E. M<hi rend="smallcaps">ac</hi>IVER, <hi rend="smallcaps">Jr</hi>.</item>
                        </list>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>The <hi rend="smallcaps">Secretary</hi>
                        <hi rend="italic">Board of Trade</hi>.</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
